1. The hole is dug out. (The hole has been dug out.)
2. Theflowers will be planted when she comes. (Theflowers will have been
planted when she comes.)
3. The letter was signed when he called. (The letter had been signed when he
called.)
4. The T-shirt is washed. (The T-shirt has been washed.)
5. Dinner was prepared when we came. (Dinner had been prepared when we
came.)
